{"type": "article", "id": 5583, "title": "Copenhagen Pendant 吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-27T07:42:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234025DuJkE90ewmVQIrGO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计工作室 Space Copenhagen 为丹麦设计品牌 &amp;tradition 带来了一款灯具作品，名为「Copenhagen Pendant」。设计团队以哥本哈根码头用的旧式吊灯为参考，创造了这款哥本哈根吊灯，拱形钢材制成的灯罩，向下向内逐渐缩小，底部收紧的开口保证了光线直射向下。表面施以不同颜色的金属亚光漆面，仿若雕塑。Copenhagen Pendant 提供 3 种 尺寸、5 种亚光颜色的选择，感兴趣的朋友可关注一下 &amp;tradition 正在升级的网站。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234024WfYmuNvSI9FKDE2b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234024WwClRHKAPThf561m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234025wkHzSshOQiYC2lKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}